---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Dropdown from "../components/Dropdown.astro";
---

<Layout title="Welcome to Astro.">
	<main>
		<section class="full-height-section">
			<h1>Register for AstroHacks 2024!</h1>

			<p class="text-center">Scroll to learn more</p>

			<svg
				class="scroll-icon"
				viewBox="0 0 48 48"
				fill="none"
				xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
			>
				<path
					d="M8 44V32.15C8 31.4833 8.15867 30.85 8.476 30.25C8.79333 29.65 9.23467 29.1667 9.8 28.8L12 27.35C12.2333 30.15 12.6 32.5333 13.1 34.5C13.6 36.4667 14.3833 38.65 15.45 41.05L8 44ZM18.45 40C17.2833 37.8 16.4167 35.4667 15.85 33C15.2833 30.5333 15 27.9833 15 25.35C15 21.1833 15.8253 17.2587 17.476 13.576C19.1267 9.89335 21.3013 7.10135 24 5.20001C26.7 7.10001 28.8753 9.89201 30.526 13.576C32.1767 17.26 33.0013 21.1847 33 25.35C33 27.95 32.7167 30.4753 32.15 32.926C31.5833 35.3767 30.7167 37.7347 29.55 40H18.45ZM24 26C25.1 26 26.042 25.6087 26.826 24.826C27.61 24.0433 28.0013 23.1013 28 22C28 20.9 27.6087 19.9587 26.826 19.176C26.0433 18.3933 25.1013 18.0013 24 18C22.9 18 21.9587 18.392 21.176 19.176C20.3933 19.96 20.0013 20.9013 20 22C20 23.1 20.392 24.042 21.176 24.826C21.96 25.61 22.9013 26.0013 24 26ZM40 44L32.55 41.05C33.6167 38.65 34.4 36.4667 34.9 34.5C35.4 32.5333 35.7667 30.15 36 27.35L38.2 28.8C38.7667 29.1667 39.2087 29.65 39.526 30.25C39.8433 30.85 40.0013 31.4833 40 32.15V44Z"
					fill="white"></path>
			</svg>
		</section>

		<hr />

		<section class="about-section">
			<h2>About AstroHacks</h2>
			<p>
				Whether you are a complete beginner who wants to dip your toes into the
				world of Computer Science, or the next Zuckerberg in the making,
				AstroHacks is for you! It’s a completely FREE coding competition for
				high school students of ANY skill level. We’ll have prizes, food, and
				above all we aim to create a space for students to hang out, learn
				coding, build projects, and have fun! Check out some pics from Assemble,
				another hackathon run by Hack Clubbers like us!
			</p>

			<div class="image-row">
				<img src="images/assemble1.png" alt="AstroHacks 2024" />
				<img src="images/assemble2.png" alt="AstroHacks 2024" />
				<img src="images/assemble3.png" alt="AstroHacks 2024" />
				<img src="images/assemble4.png" alt="AstroHacks 2024" />
			</div>

			<p>
				Interested? Excited? Ready to compete with existing friends or new
				friends? <a href="">Register today!</a>
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class="dropdowns-section">
			<h2>FAQs</h2>
			<Dropdown
				title="Who can participate?"
				body="Any high schooler can participate!"
			/>
			<Dropdown title="When and where is this hackathon?" body="">
				<p class="text-left">
					AstroHacks 2024 will be held at the Boys and Girls Club of Irvine, 295
					E Yale Loop, Irvine, CA 92604. The event will be held on April 13th
					for 12 hours, 9am to 9pm.
				</p>
				<br />
				<p class="text-left">9am - Welcome in/Breakfast</p>
				<p class="text-left">10am - Opening ceremony</p>
				<p class="text-left">11am - Workshop #1</p>
				<p class="text-left">12pm - Find/Organize your team</p>
				<p class="text-left">1pm - Lunch/Start Hacking</p>
				<p class="text-left">4pm - Icebreaker or Workshop #2</p>
				<p class="text-left">5pm - Dinner/Continue Hacking</p>
				<p class="text-left">7:30 - Presentations</p>
				<p class="text-left">8:30 - Closing Ceremony- Finish by 9pm</p>
			</Dropdown>

			<Dropdown
				title="Does this event cost money?"
				body="Nope, this event will be completely free!"
			/>

			<Dropdown
				title="What should I bring?"
				body="A form of identification (Student ID, Drivers License, etc.), laptop, charger(s), and any other items that you think you'll need."
			/>

			<Dropdown
				title="What if I have dietary restrictions?"
				body="We will provide food along with vegetarian options but unfortunately we are not able to provide vegan options. If you prefer to bring your own food or you are vegan, we recommend you to bring your own meals. We are very sorry for the inconvenience."
			/>

			<Dropdown
				title="I have more questions..."
				body="I have a lot of ways you can contact me! You can shoot me a Discord friend request @congo17, a text on Slack @Chris (the profile picture with an anime guy smiling), text my phone at +1(951) 595 - 2909, or email me on my personal (because our org email is kinda iffy sometimes): chris981lee@outlook.com"
			/>
		</section>

		<style>
			main {
				margin: auto;
				padding: 1rem;
				width: 75%;
				max-width: calc(100% - 2rem);
				color: white;
				font-size: 20px;
				line-height: 1.6;
			}

			hr {
				border: 0;
				height: 1px;
				background: white;
				margin: 2em 0;
			}

			.full-height-section {
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				justify-content: center;
				align-items: center;
				height: 100vh;
				padding: 2rem;
			}

			.dropdowns {
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				align-items: center;
				gap: 1rem;
			}

			.scroll-icon {
				position: absolute;
				bottom: 20px;
				left: 50%;
				transform: translateX(-50%) rotate(180deg);
				width: 50px; /* Adjust as needed */
				height: 50px; /* Adjust as needed */
			}

			.about-section {
				margin: 2rem 0;
			}

			.about-section p {
				margin: 1rem 0;
			}

			.image-row {
				display: flex;
				flex-wrap: wrap;
				justify-content: center;
				gap: 1rem;
			}

			.image-row img {
				width: 200px;
				height: 200px;
				object-fit: cover;
				border-radius: 10px;
				border: 1px solid white;
			}
		</style>
	</main>
</Layout>
